7 An Act relating to school district elections;
amending 26 O.S. 2021, Sections 13A-103 and 13A-105,
8 which relate to election dates and declaration of
candidacy; modifying permissible dates for certain
9 elections; modifying dates for filing for certain
office; and providing an effective date.
10
11
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 26 O.S. 2021, Section 13A-103, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 13A-103. A. 1. The general election of members of the
16 board of education of every school district and technology center
17 school district shall be conducted on the first second Tuesday of
18 April November of each odd-numbered year, and on the first Tuesday
19 after the first Monday of November in each even-numbered year.
20 2. The primary election of members of the board of education of
21 every school district and technology center school district, if
22 necessary, shall be conducted on the second Tuesday in February
23 September of each odd-numbered year, except in any year when a
24 Presidential Preferential Primary is held in February, then the
